00:29:06.420 --> 00:29:09.000
This is something that almost
every guest on the podcast

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:10.230
touches on in some capacity.

00:29:10.230 --> 00:29:13.980
Folks that are successful are
folks that build a network.

00:29:13.980 --> 00:29:15.761
People hire people
that they know,

00:29:15.761 --> 00:29:17.010
that they're comfortable with.

00:29:17.010 --> 00:29:21.030
And one way to do that is by
meeting people and forming

00:29:21.030 --> 00:29:23.190
that personal relationship,
so I appreciate that.

00:29:23.190 --> 00:29:24.900
And thank you guys
for all that insight.

